Introduction

Laurence is a Taiwanese-South Korean singer under n.CH Entertainment. He is a member of the boy group n.SSign.

In 2022, Laurence participated in the Channel A survival show Stars Awakening. Unfortunately, he was eliminated in episode 11.

On July 1, 2023, n.CH Entertainment announced that n.SSign would reorganize as a permanent boy group with the addition of 3 new members. On July 8, Laurence was then announced as the second new member that will be added to the group with the release of his concept photo.
